": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36051, "box": [214.69458128078819, 161.2044773013871, 721.7313144499179, 26.253468474148917], "id_box_line": 5, "box_line": [214.69458128078819, 176.7671957755358, 674.0096876026273, 10.690750000000207], "text": "of the respective assets, which vary according to their general classification, type of construction and function.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36052, "box": [229.0001477832512, 192.34268474148791, 662.9094088669951, 10.69074999999998], "id_box_line": 6, "box_line": [229.0001477832512, 192.34268474148791, 662.9094088669951, 10.69074999999998], "text": "Maintenance and repairs, including minor renewals and improvements, are charged to income as incurred.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36053, "box": [214.69458128078819, 239.05636822194197, 737.6500693760263, 26.266238965952084], "id_box_line": 9, "box_line": [214.69458128078819, 239.05636822194197, 737.6500693760263, 10.69074999999998], "text": "Receivable accounts recognized by the lessors in finance lease transactions are recorded as lease receivables and, assets", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36053, "box": [214.69458128078819, 239.05636822194197, 737.6500693760263, 26.266238965952084], "id_box_line": 10, "box_line": [214.69458128078819, 254.63185718789407, 607.0943382594418, 10.69074999999998], "text": "acquired by lessees in finance lease transactions are recorded in the corresponding asset accounts.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36054, "box": [214.69458128078819, 301.345540668348, 366.6733004926109, 10.69076292559896], "id_box_line": 13, "box_line": [214.69458128078819, 301.345540668348, 366.6733004926109, 10.69076292559896], "text": "The Company and most consolidated subsidiaries in Japan:", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36055, "box": [214.69458128078819, 316.9210296343001, 712.4986900656816, 57.40440762925596], "id_box_line": 14, "box_line": [229.0001477832512, 316.9210296343001, 692.9625435139573, 10.69076292559896], "text": "Pension costs of major defined benefit plans are based on annual contributions calculated by a projected benefit", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36055, "box": [214.69458128078819, 316.9210296343001, 712.4986900656816, 57.40440762925596], "id_box_line": 15, "box_line": [214.69458128078819, 332.4965186002522, 712.4986900656816, 10.69076292559896], "text": "valuation method. Accrued severance benefits are stated at the present value of the vested benefit obligation which", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36055, "box": [214.69458128078819, 316.9210296343001, 712.4986900656816, 57.40440762925596], "id_box_line": 16, "box_line": [214.69458128078819, 348.05922414880206, 672.666011904762, 10.69076292559896], "text": "would be required to be paid if all employees voluntarily terminated their services at the balance sheet dates.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36055, "box": [214.69458128078819, 316.9210296343001, 712.4986900656816, 57.40440762925596], "id_box_line": 17, "box_line": [214.69458128078819, 363.6346743379571, 284.31478612479475, 10.69076292559896], "text": "Most consolidated subsidiaries outside Japan: ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36056, "box": [229.0001477832512, 379.2101633039092, 576.821527093596, 10.69076292559896], "id_box_line": 18, "box_line": [229.0001477832512, 379.2101633039092, 576.821527093596, 10.69076292559896], "text": "Pension costs of major defined benefit plans are calculated by a projected unit credit method.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36057, "box": [214.69308333333333, 425.9238080075662, 736.7760254515599, 72.97989659520806], "id_box_line": 21, "box_line": [214.69458128078819, 425.9238080075662, 733.3845209359606, 10.69076292559896], "text": "Certain computers manufactured by the Group are sold to Japan Electronic Computer Company Limited (\u201cJECC\u201d) and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36057, "box": [214.69308333333333, 425.9238080075662, 736.7760254515599, 72.97989659520806], "id_box_line": 22, "box_line": [214.69308333333333, 441.4992969735183, 719.1273431855502, 10.69076292559896], "text": "other leasing companies and financial institutions for leasing to the ultimate users under contracts which require that", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36057, "box": [214.69308333333333, 425.9238080075662, 736.7760254515599, 72.97989659520806], "id_box_line": 23, "box_line": [214.69308333333333, 457.0619637452711, 736.7760254515599, 10.690762925599074], "text": "the Group repurchase the computers if they are returned by the users after a certain period. Based on past experience,", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36057, "box": [214.69308333333333, 425.9238080075662, 736.7760254515599, 72.97989659520806], "id_box_line": 24, "box_line": [214.69308333333333, 472.6374527112232, 697.3691514778326, 10.69076292559896], "text": "an estimated amount for the loss arising from such repurchases is provided at the point of sale and is charged to", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36057, "box": [214.69308333333333, 425.9238080075662, 736.7760254515599, 72.97989659520806], "id_box_line": 25, "box_line": [214.69308333333333, 488.2129416771752, 48.57289860426931, 10.690762925599074], "text": "income.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36058, "box": [214.69308333333333, 534.9265863808323, 722.3417869458129, 26.266251891551008], "id_box_line": 28, "box_line": [214.69308333333333, 534.9265863808323, 722.3417869458129, 10.690762925598904], "text": "The Group has adopted the balance sheet liability method of tax effect accounting in order to recognize the effect of", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36058, "box": [214.69308333333333, 534.9265863808323, 722.3417869458129, 26.266251891551008], "id_box_line": 29, "box_line": [214.69308333333333, 550.5020753467843, 657.8500829228243, 10.690762925599017], "text": "all temporary differences in the recognition of assets and liabilities for tax and financial reporting purposes.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JDHMHK+Delta-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 36059, "box": [214.69308333333333, 597.2157329760403, 733.0451600985222, 26.266238965952084], "id_box_line": 32, "box_line": [214.69308333333333, 597.2157329760403, 733.0451600985222, 10.690750000000037], "text": "Basic earn